  "title": "Class 4 Driver (Towing Service) #76248",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Towing Service</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Class 4 Driver (Towing Service)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Redhill</li><li>Working Hours: 4 days (Monday – Friday), Day Shift 7am-7pm; Night shift 7pm-7am</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $4000 + AWS + Incentive + Allowance</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide vehicle recovery services for breakdowns, accidents, or unattended vehicles on roads and expressways.</li><li>Assist motorists with flat tyre replacement when needed.</li><li>Perform other duties as required during on-road assignments.</li><li>Manage traffic and assist with incident management as needed.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Valid Singapore Class 4 driving licence required.</li><li>Minimum qualification: NTC in Vehicle Mechanic or higher.</li><li>Able to work rotating day and night shifts, including weekends and public holidays.</li><li>Experience in towing or vehicle recovery is an advantage.</li><li>Knowledge of basic vehicle repair or maintenance is a plus.</li><li>Candidates with no related experience but a willingness to learn and a positive attitude are welcome.</li><li>Able to start work immediately or on short notice is preferred.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76248 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
